br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">希望男朋友唔好見到呢個怨氣post 唔想佢難做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8eeb4c928ed94f80537624b52bbc2187df22f82f","tid":800133,"uid":5572,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"On99 呢啲臭閪就指撚住佢個頭屌啦 你條仔唔幫拖就屌埋佢"},{"pid":"35939f5afdc6cb12733434fedc920149ab36f625","tid":800133,"uid":178332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:17:51.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼咩差啲以為你四個一齊住<br />\n你以後又唔係同佢家姐過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話知佢啦"},{"pid":"aca2e02e7745d961acb52e1eb7cf45af4620316a","tid":800133,"uid":39177,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:18:10.000Z","msg":"睇完最後細字果句,只能夠講你抵撚死,做野啦"},{"pid":"c76bc237fbf5d124eb560919d3a15cc0510273fb","tid":800133,"uid":77478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eeb4c928ed94f80537624b52bbc2187df22f82f","tid":800133,"uid":5572,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"On99 呢啲臭閪就指撚住佢個頭屌啦 你條仔唔幫拖就屌埋佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"條仔話覺得同佢溝通唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5deebf59c0c486a8d06a22ff8d2792fa8ab813","tid":800133,"uid":5482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:28:37.000Z","msg":"咁係佢家姐未來老公慘姐<br />\n你又唔洗同佢過人世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d57464e1e964e7db8c356ca366fbbab4efec20","tid":800133,"uid":77478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35939f5afdc6cb12733434fedc920149ab36f625","tid":800133,"uid":178332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:17:51.000Z","msg":"嚇鬼咩差啲以為你四個一齊住<br />\n你以後又唔係同佢家姐過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話知佢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:30:37.000Z","msg":"其實可以既話我真係唔想面阻阻<br />\n但佢既然咁樣擺大家姐款屌鳩我 我都唔會再同佢好黎好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07b1d3d2936e0d68cac621f4791e3baaa45131b","tid":800133,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"佢擺明慣曬係咁 不過平時有兩老幫佢做家務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137244857f61c849e722b1b36e82d3578cf4a589","tid":800133,"uid":5572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c76bc237fbf5d124eb560919d3a15cc0510273fb","tid":800133,"uid":77478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eeb4c928ed94f80537624b52bbc2187df22f82f","tid":800133,"uid":5572,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"On99 呢啲臭閪就指撚住佢個頭屌啦 你條仔唔幫拖就屌埋佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:24:40.000Z","msg":"條仔話覺得同佢溝通唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:38:49.000Z","msg":"咁就唔好理 咩都唔好洗 到最後老豆老母番黎都係死你條仔同佢家姐 條仔比人屌個陣叫佢同老母講你每次上黎都有汁下屋 然後順手爆埋家姐條仔過左好多晚夜 屌左好多次閪 完"},{"pid":"25707824eacfc412a36e398d23c13a0aea0058dd","tid":800133,"uid":77478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e07b1d3d2936e0d68cac621f4791e3baaa45131b","tid":800133,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"佢擺明慣曬係咁 不過平時有兩老幫佢做家務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:39:44.000Z","msg":"平時兩老在家 佢連衫都唔自己洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3413e3151822e667d0ab17c74facdb0c584583e","tid":800133,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"咁佢負責煮<br />\n你/你條仔負責有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b8b13abfbda6877120ec5284e702d7161243f4","tid":800133,"uid":54787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"